{"tid":2365403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"風水撚 建築撚入 K11 Musea 蛇陣 [2]","createTime":"2021-01-13T17:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T21:48:37.000Z","uid":14953,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1608d330c4e410ade7ff3f30c7d0145c11ce3449","tid":2365403,"uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"要加返建築撚入，因為班風水撚好撚惡，話你唔係信風水就唔可以討論。<br />\n<br />\n上文係<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHMFEPU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHMFEPU</a><br />\n主要有兩派，一派係風水撚，覺得香港多左好多蛇形建築，係蛇陣。中共有心落order 迫害佢地。<br />\n一派係建築撚，覺得佢地on撚鳩。現代建築多左freeform curve/ organic form 係因為建築技術進步左，同受到現代建築師影響，例如zaha hadid, Frank Gehry。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎所有人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c41ff1c0cfd69a382c662e0c80d1a2900bdba53","tid":2365403,"uid":63785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"去撚到2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd21190754bc824f5228cb7608df3f9dd27f273","tid":2365403,"uid":14953,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"風水撚就話K11係有心整蛇陣搞臭香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BsBAH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BsBAH6.png&h=2c86f375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ov39bgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fov39bgs.jpg&h=6ab91360&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHNenn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHNenn7.jpg&h=a5416369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dw2NHn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdw2NHn8.jpg&h=348001ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建築撚就話全世界都有呢D建築，叫佢地唔好被害妄想症發作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcmCDGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt