":14,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1608d330c4e410ade7ff3f30c7d0145c11ce3449","tid":2365403,"uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:06:46.000Z","msg":"要加返建築撚入，因為班風水撚好撚惡，話你唔係信風水就唔可以討論。<br />\n<br />\n上文係<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aHMFEPU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aHMFEPU</a><br />\n主要有兩派，一派係風水撚，覺得香港多左好多蛇形建築，係蛇陣。中共有心落order 迫害佢地。<br />\n一派係建築撚，覺得佢地on撚鳩。現代建築多左freeform curve/ organic form 係因為建築技術進步左，同受到現代建築師影響，例如zaha hadid, Frank Gehry。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎所有人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"風水唔講<br />\n但建築撚果個point真係無奚之談<br />\n呢D建築物明明係跟金主老細order做野<br />\n又關咩個人風格事？<br />\n<br />\n其次就係唔理你咩藝術咩影響<br />\n而家整出嚟果件野係公認咁樣令人不安<br />\n<br />\n三來就係香港真係好多好似蛇嘅建築<br />\n過份巧合已經唔係巧合<br />\n<br />\n另外講到風水，禮賓府出晒名連鬼佬都知有問題<br />\n你可以唔信風水，但風水同迷信係兩件事<br />\n某D風水可以用西方科學理論解釋到<br />\n<br />\n唔好無知仲咁大聲"},{"pid":"6b074f9be2e4f712a8e3488b49e50c8bfe42ec9e","tid":2365403,"uid":79081,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"25d7d5562aa17f0861ff0a4e4c71f84849b57431","tid":2365403,"uid":35776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cd21190754bc824f5228cb7608df3f9dd27f273","tid":2365403,"uid":14953,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"風水撚就話K11係有心整蛇陣搞臭香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BsBAH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BsBAH6.png&h=2c86f375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ov39bgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fov39bgs.jpg&h=6ab91360&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHNenn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHNenn7.jpg&h=a5416369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dw2NHn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdw2NHn8.jpg&h=348001ee